---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { RAILWAY_REFERRAL_LINK } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead 
			title="About Railway Platform Guide" 
			description="Learn about our mission to help developers discover Railway's powerful deployment platform through comprehensive guides and tutorials." 
		/>
		<style>
			body main {
				max-width: min(1024px, calc(100vw - 32px)) !important;
				margin: 0 auto !important;
				padding: 0 16px !important;
				width: auto !important;
			}
			.hero-image {
				width: 100%;
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
			}
			.hero-image img {
				display: block;
				margin: 0 auto;
				border-radius: 12px;
				box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
				width: 100%;
				max-width: 720px;
			}
			.content {
				max-width: min(720px, calc(100vw - 64px));
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 24px 0;
				color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
			}
			.title {
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
				text-align: center;
				line-height: 1;
			}
			.title h1 {
				margin: 0;
				color: rgb(var(--black));
			}
		</style>
	</head>

	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<article>
				<div class="hero-image">
					<img width={1020} height={510} src="/blog-placeholder-about.jpg" alt="About Railway Platform Guide" />
				</div>
				<div class="content">
					<div class="title">
						<h1>About Railway Platform Guide</h1>
						<hr />
					</div>
	<p>
		Welcome to Railway Platform Guide, your comprehensive resource for learning about Railway's powerful deployment platform. Our mission is to help developers discover how Railway can transform their development workflow.
	</p>

	<h2>Why We Created This Guide</h2>
	<p>
		Modern app deployment shouldn't be complex. After experiencing the simplicity and power of Railway firsthand, we wanted to share this knowledge with the developer community. Railway represents a significant shift in how we think about deployment - from complex infrastructure management to simple, developer-focused solutions.
	</p>

	<h2>What You'll Find Here</h2>
	<p>
		Our guides cover everything you need to know about Railway:
	</p>
	<ul>
		<li>Step-by-step deployment tutorials for popular frameworks</li>
		<li>Database setup and configuration guides</li>
		<li>Best practices for production deployments</li>
		<li>Honest comparisons with other platforms</li>
		<li>Real-world examples and use cases</li>
	</ul>

	<h2>Our Approach</h2>
	<p>
		We believe in providing honest, practical guidance based on real-world experience. Every tutorial is tested, and every recommendation comes from actual usage. We focus on helping you understand not just how to use Railway, but why it's a great choice for modern development.
	</p>

	<h2>Get Started with Railway</h2>
	<p>
		Ready to experience the future of deployment? <a href={RAILWAY_REFERRAL_LINK} target="_blank" rel="noopener">Start your Railway journey today</a> and see why thousands of developers are making the switch.
	</p>

	<p>
		<strong>Questions or suggestions?</strong> We'd love to hear from you! Railway has an active community of developers who are always happy to help.
	</p>
				</div>
			</article>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
